VALUES ('hina-matsuri-katsuura', 'Katsuura Big Hina Matsuri', 'かつうらビッグひな祭り', 'Katsuura', 'Chiba', 'kanto', 3, '03-01', '03-03', '["03-03"]', '["traditional"]', 'Around 30,000 hina dolls are displayed on the steps of Tomisaki Shrine and throughout the town. A spectacular sight celebrating Girls'' Day.', '約3万体のひな人形が遠見岬神社の石段や町中に飾られる。', 80000, 'JR Katsuura Station', 35.1528, 140.3178, 'The 60-step stone staircase display at Tomisaki Shrine is the most photogenic spot.', '', 1, '2026-03-29T00:00:00Z');

