VALUES ('izu-kawazu-sakura', 'Kawazu Cherry Blossom Festival', '河津桜まつり', 'Kawazu', 'Shizuoka', 'chubu', 3, '03-01', '03-10', '["03-01"]', '["cherry_blossom"]', 'Early-blooming Kawazu cherry trees line the riverbank creating a stunning pink tunnel. One of the first cherry blossom events of the year on the Izu Peninsula.', '早咲きの河津桜が川沿いに並ぶ伊豆の春の風物詩。', 300000, 'Izukyu Kawazu Station', 34.7467, 138.9964, 'Peak bloom is usually late February to early March. Check forecasts.', '', 1, '2026-03-29T00:00:00Z');

