VALUES ('ohara-jidai-gyoretsu', 'Ohara Festival', 'おはら祭', 'Kagoshima', 'Kagoshima', 'kyushu', 11, '11-02', '11-03', '["11-03"]', '["dance","modern"]', 'Kagoshima''s biggest festival with over 20,000 dancers performing the Ohara-bushi dance through the main street. A lively celebration of Satsuma culture.', '2万人が踊るおはら節。鹿児島最大の祭り。', 300000, 'JR Kagoshima-Chuo Station, tram', 31.5889, 130.5583, 'November 3 (Culture Day) is the main day. Anyone can join in the dancing.', '', 1, '2026-03-29T00:00:00Z');

