VALUES ('sounkyo-hyobaku', 'Sounkyo Hyobaku Festival', '層雲峡氷瀑まつり', 'Kamikawa', 'Hokkaido', 'hokkaido', 1, '01-23', '03-16', '["02-01"]', '["snow","lantern"]', 'Ice sculptures and frozen waterfalls illuminated in colorful lights at Sounkyo Gorge. One of Hokkaido''s most scenic winter events.', '層雲峡の氷瀑がライトアップされる冬の祭典。', 120000, 'JR Kamikawa Station, bus to Sounkyo', 43.7283, 143.1419, 'Best combined with a visit to Sounkyo onsen. Night illumination is magical.', '', 1, '2026-03-29T00:00:00Z');

